{"tid":154016,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美職聯零下7度暴風雪下作賽超熱血","createTime":"2017-03-13T03:54:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-13T04:29:08.000Z","uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9928637c6e68d032f4cef71856c0d2711ca51e23","tid":154016,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T03:54:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LQ2lUIKbDXA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLQ2lUIKbDXA&d=HFtALxS4LzZAkeshXsvvbvjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=bf1bd664\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LQ2lUIKbDXA</a><br />\n<br />\n周日兩支美職聯今季新軍對壘，明尼蘇達聯首次主場出擊，就俾阿特蘭大聯狂炒1:6，但戰果都係其次，因為兩軍頂住零下7度喺風雪下作賽，球迷又坐爆35,000人主場館，絕對值得肅然起敬！<br />\n<br />\n其實美職聯賽會日前得知天氣預報後已經好貼心，專登推出一款橙色足球大派用場，明尼蘇達聯陣中唔少北歐兵仲話，更差嘅天氣狀況見得多，can't hold them back anymore喎！不過，教過巴塞隆拿、見慣大場面嘅阿特蘭大聯主帥馬天奴，就話大開眼界：「我初頭真係有啲擔心場波會點發展，因為我從來未帶過隊喺雪中作戰。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://usatsbi.files.wordpress.com/2017/03/atlanta-united-minnesota-united-03122017.jpg?w=1000&amp;h=667\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fusatsbi.files.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F03%2Fatlanta-united-minnesota-united-03122017.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D667&h=271a258a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.mlsdigital.net/www.mlssoccer.com/7/article/325156/620x350.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.mlsdigital.net%2Fwww.mlssoccer.com%2F7%2Farticle%2F325156%2F620x350.jpg&h=0d851d81&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89d96e26c08e871ba45b889086bc3959f5d273f5","tid":154016,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T03:56:24.000Z","msg":"做咩唔學某玩具咁喺冷氣房踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"348ed30abd5b827001809e95fca54901e6732f0b","tid":154016,"uid":9069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T04:05:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做咩唔學某玩具咁喺冷氣房踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" cla